jcalendar

An implementation of JQuery's Datepicker and Fullcalendar
with the use of CodeIgniter.

See http://jcalendar-oif2ot3o.dotcloud.com/ for a working demo.

The demo runs on dotcloud.com, and it's running in nginx.
See nginx.conf for redirect uri method. 


FEATURES

It features events (dates) rendering from a database.
It works with Datepicker and Fullcalendar in day mode.
It records drops/resizes of events into a database. 

DEPENDENCIES

* Codeigniter
* PHP5


